      <title>Mastodon Interview</title>
      <link>https://ashfurrow.com/blog/mastodon-interview/</link>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://joinmastodon.org"&gt;Mastodon&lt;/a&gt;: still a thing. And &lt;a href="https://mastodon.technology"&gt;my instance&lt;/a&gt;, also still a thing! Recently, one of the users on mastodon.technology sat down and &lt;a href="http://www.smays.com/2017/06/ash-furrow/"&gt;interviewed me&lt;/a&gt; about the platform and the project.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class='embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9'&gt;&lt;iframe src='//www.youtube.com/embed/x3FEs8sgXjE' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;My participation in Mastodon hasn&amp;rsquo;t been steady, but neither was my participation in Twitter at first. I&amp;rsquo;m still finding my feet and my voice there. I still don&amp;rsquo;t know what the future holds; this is still an experiment, but I&amp;rsquo;m excited to see where we end up together.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
